{"tid":178381,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"逢7必股災，拆解股災必要條件","createTime":"2017-03-29T13:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T01:30:07.000Z","uid":80270,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4754312634fe33a6269995eb3c4b52b9674435f2","tid":178381,"uid":80270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:33:04.000Z","msg":"【小統計】<br />\n好多好多好多股民，都擔心今年係繼97，07，之後既股災年，小編就睇返之前次股災年，再加上15年既港股大時代，睇下搵唔搵到股災先兆喇。<br />\n<br />\nCool........睇完之後發覺左一樣野，依三次所謂股災見頂，係見頂前個一個月，整月既升幅原來非常可觀，平均有成12%，就算拎97個次升得最少既做例子，都有成7.69%。<br />\n<br />\n所以呢，今年會唔會股災，我諗人無人識答，但等無喇喇有個月升左2，3千點既時候，就要提高警覺喇。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50a8A90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50a8A90.jpg&h=2acbb07a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/investeasywin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finvesteasywin&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e15d539b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/investeasywin</a>"},{"pid":"0b22b28830b90bce58b7aadec54d3a7d8d80d462","tid":178381,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcff8d611255aca524dadf3675a4a0cf8545d55d","tid":178381,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"要股災必先大升係咩廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大升就自然會大跌<br />\n<br />\n你牛皮市大跌就話姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e098466bc9f2ac14ba93aec6516fc3b1abdaaa80","tid":178381,"uid":56752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:54:38.000Z","msg":"明了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係大升就一定跌<br />\n唔升就未必唔跌<br />\n跌就一定唔跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}